name: testPreviewDescriptionFromEditInformationPage
description: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for MultiConfiguration Project
descriptionHtml: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for MultiConfiguration Project

testStage.description: Verification of presence preview description of build from Edit Information Page for MultiConfiguration Project

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click Edit Buld Information on the side bar menu
Input the description 'Description in the 'Description' field on the Edit Build Information page
Click on the 'Preview' button on the Edit Build Information page
Get Preview text on the Edit Build Information page
Logout from instance http://localhost:8081/
